Class OutputQuantityOFZones

  • java.lang.Object
    • sensitivity_input.OutputQuantityOFZones

  • public class OutputQuantityOFZones
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds a summary of a particular quantity over several zones. It reflects a NANDRAD output file with a table of the particular quantity in the regarded zones.
    Author:
    Frank Noack
